{"type":"text","timestamp":1775851431199,"sessionID":"ses_287080b2cfferkvBPF2P0Q3FTV","part":{"id":"prt_d78fe318700181n7cJk3AOPmeM","messageID":"msg_d78fddfd3001feBxNxDtOcJn7q","sessionID":"ses_287080b2cfferkvBPF2P0Q3FTV","type":"text","text":"I've created the delta-spec.md for AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器. The spec contains **652 lines** with comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering:\n\n## Summary of Requirements Covered\n\n### Core Requirements\n1. **Controller Manager Bootstrap** - Initialization, config loading, graceful shutdown\n2. **AgentRuntime Reconciler** - CRUD operations, status management, sandbox lifecycle\n3. **CodeInterpreter Reconciler** - Warm pool support, auth configuration, ready state\n4. **Event-Driven Watch & Reconciliation** - Resource watches, event handling, reconnection\n5. **Reconcile Queue with Rate Limiting** - Work queue, concurrent workers, max retries\n\n### Resilience & Reliability\n6. **Exponential Backoff** - Retry delays, jitter, success reset\n7. **Finalizer Handling** - Cleanup, multi-finalizer support, failure handling\n8. **Status Updates & Condition Management** - Phase transitions, condition updates, conflict handling\n9. **OwnerReference Management** - GC integration, cascade deletion\n\n### Integration & Observability\n10. **WorkloadManager Service Integration** - Store updates, shared informers\n11. **Metrics & Observability** - Prometheus metrics, structured logging\n12. **Error Handling & Recovery** - API errors, RBAC, panics, invalid specs\n13. **Leader Election (Preparation)** - HA deployment readiness\n\n## Key Features\n- **16 requirements** with **80+ acceptance scenarios**\n- **File index** with 14 source files\n- **Dependencies** including controller-runtime v0.20.0+\n- **Data types** (ReconcilerConfig, Finalizer constants)\n- **Metrics reference** with 5 Prometheus metrics\n- Full integration with existing AR-004 (HTTP Service), AR-005 (Sandbox Creation), and AR-006 (Lifecycle Management)\n\nThe file is located at: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md`","time":{"start":1775851431196,"end":1775851431196}}}
